                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 12.676,
                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 79454,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in Costle, the Administrator of the Environmental Protection Agency against Pacific Legal Foundation will be announced by Mr. Justice Blackmun."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 12.676,
                        "stop": 103.146,
                        "byte_start": 79454,
                        "byte_stop": 441302,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15045,
                            "name": "Harry A. Blackmun",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/harry_a_blackmun",
                            "last_name": "Blackmun",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2689,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": 13755600,
                                    "date_end": 775890000,
                                    "appointing_president": "Richard Nixon",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2689"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32712,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 50281,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/harry_a_blackmun.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 8821,
                            "identifier": "harry_a_blackmun"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 12.676,
                                "stop": 17.634,
                                "byte_start": 79454,
                                "byte_stop": 99307,
                                "text": "Well, this case comes to us from the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 17.634,
                                "stop": 25.227,
                                "byte_start": 99307,
                                "byte_stop": 129609,
                                "text": "It has to do with Los Angeles discharged of its sewage into the Pacific Ocean."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 25.227,
                                "stop": 41.477,
                                "byte_start": 129609,
                                "byte_stop": 194602,
                                "text": "Under the Federal Water Pollution Control Act Amendments of 1972, the Environmental Protection Agency, upon specified conditions may issue a permit for the discharge of pollutants."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 41.477,
                                "stop": 45.06,
                                "byte_start": 194602,
                                "byte_stop": 208917,
                                "text": "The permit in fact was issued to the City."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 45.06,
                                "stop": 56.984,
                                "byte_start": 208917,
                                "byte_stop": 256669,
                                "text": "The case centers, however, on the ultimate termination of the Pacific Ocean discharge and the possible alternative deposit of sludge in a landfill site."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 56.984,
                                "stop": 70.682,
                                "byte_start": 256669,
                                "byte_stop": 311421,
                                "text": "The issue was essentially one of the administrative laws and it involves the right to a public hearing and concerns expressed by environmentalist who are opposed to bringing the ocean discharge to an end."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 70.682,
                                "stop": 88.451,
                                "byte_start": 311421,
                                "byte_stop": 382579,
                                "text": "The Court of Appeals held that EPA was required to justify every failure to hold a hearing on a permit action by proof that the material facts supporting the Act and I quote \u0022are not subject to dispute.\u0022"
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 88.451,
                                "stop": 90.912,
                                "byte_start": 382579,
                                "byte_stop": 392401,
                                "text": "We disagree with that conclusion."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 90.912,
                                "stop": 103.146,
                                "byte_start": 392401,
                                "byte_stop": 441302,
                                "text": "And in an opinion filed today, the reasons for our disagreement are set forth at some length. The judgment of the Court of Appeals is therefore reversed."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 103.146,
                        "stop": 106.542,
